# TTB Label Checker - Frontend Environment Variables
# ===================================================

# Cloud Functions API Endpoint (OPTIONAL)
# ----------------------------------------
# By default, the app automatically uses the correct endpoint:
# - Production: Relative URL '/api' (via Firebase Hosting rewrites)
# - Development: 'http://localhost:5001/ttb-label-checker/us-east4' (Firebase emulator)
#
# Only override if you need a custom endpoint:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5001/ttb-label-checker/us-east4
#
# Or to test against production from local dev:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://us-east4-ttb-label-checker.cloudfunctions.net

# Notes:
# - No environment variables are required! Defaults work for most cases
# - Firebase Hosting rewrites handle production routing (see firebase.json)
# - The region (us-east4) matches the backend deployment in functions/main.py
